s:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_TOD-1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_TOD-1-200x200.png 200w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_TOD-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_TOD-1.png 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" \/>DiGT \u2013 Signalisation num\u00e9rique de d\u00e9c\u00e8s<\/h3>\n<div>\n<div>Le signalement num\u00e9rique de d\u00e9c\u00e8s permet de simplifier consid\u00e9rablement les processus de signalement des diff\u00e9rents avis de d\u00e9c\u00e8s (constatation provisoire du d\u00e9c\u00e8s, certificat de d\u00e9c\u00e8s, certificat d&#8217;autopsie, acte de d\u00e9c\u00e8s). Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 un appel de param\u00e8tres configur\u00e9 dans le SIH, les donn\u00e9es sont transmises une fois par jour au bureau d&#8217;\u00e9tat civil responsable selon les exigences l\u00e9gales. La transmission du signalement est confirm\u00e9e par l&#8217;envoi d&#8217;un accus\u00e9 de r\u00e9ception aux \u00e9tablissements ayant effectu\u00e9 le signalement.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-29 fusion_builder_column_1_5 1_5 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:20%;--awb-spacing-right-large:9.6%;--awb-spacing-left-large:9.6%;--awb-width-medium:20%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:9.6%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:9.6%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-30 fusion_builder_column_1_5 1_5 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:20%;--awb-spacing-right-large:9.6%;--awb-spacing-left-large:9.6%;--awb-width-medium:20%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:9.6%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:9.6%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-31 fusion_builder_column_2_3 2_3 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:66.666666666667%;--awb-spacing-right-large:2.88%;--awb-spacing-left-large:2.88%;--awb-width-medium:66.666666666667%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:2.88%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:2.88%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-13\"><h3><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-824 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1-66x66.png 66w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1-200x200.png 200w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/vertama.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/vt_icons_BEBEPO-1.png 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\" \/>DuBA \u2013 Instruction d&#8217;h\u00e9bergement num\u00e9rique<\/h3>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>La solution DuBA sert \u00e0 signaler aux autorit\u00e9s les mesures de contrainte prescrites par les m\u00e9decins pour les patients.<br \/>\nLa communication entre les h\u00f4pitaux et les tribunaux est soumise \u00e0 des exigences de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 strictes. Pour toutes les collectivit\u00e9s de droit public, beBPo (bo\u00eete postale \u00e9lectronique sp\u00e9ciale pour les autorit\u00e9s) est une proc\u00e9dure d&#8217;adressage et de cryptage sp\u00e9ciale qui relie notre solution \u00e0 l&#8217;infrastructure du SIH, de mani\u00e8re similaire aux proc\u00e9dures de notification de DEMIS.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Vous \u00eates int\u00e9ress\u00e9 par nos services ? Nous nous ferons un plaisir de vous conseiller.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":10,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"100-width.php","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Healthcare Services - VERTAMA GMBH<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Vertama digitalisiert und automatisiert klinische Meldevorg\u00e4nge, wie Infektionsmeldungen oder Bettenbelegmeldungen, durch die Entwicklung und Implementierung von barrierefreien, digitalen Workflows.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/vertama.com\/fr\/healthcare-services-2\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Healthcare Services - VERTAMA GMBH\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Vertama digitalisiert und automatisiert klinische Meldevorg\u00e4nge, wie Infektionsmeldungen oder Bettenbelegmeldungen, durch die Entwicklung und Implementierung von barrierefreien, digitalen Workflows.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/verta